sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI
    participant Renderer

    User->>CLI: bmermaid input.mmd -o output.svg
    CLI->>CLI: Parse arguments
    CLI->>CLI: Read input file
    CLI->>Renderer: renderMermaid(code, options)
    Renderer->>Renderer: Apply theme
    Renderer->>Renderer: Generate SVG
    Renderer-->>CLI: Return SVG string
    CLI->>CLI: Write to output file
    CLI-->>User: Done!
